O sceduler einai o ipefthinos gia to se poion node tha paei to kathw pod analoga me ta resouses tou kathe node pou exoum 
mporoume na dilosoume manual kai emeis vevea se poion node tha treksei to kathw pod me to na dilosoume to "nodeName: node01"

SOS
o scheduler paanda einai sto namespace kube-system
kubectl get pods -n kube-system
---
apiVersion: v1
kind: Pod
metadata:
  name: nginx
spec:
  nodeName: node01
  containers:
  -  image: nginx
     name: nginx

